  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nChanged the version in docker-compose.yml from 2.2.1 to 2.3.0, watched logs and saw failures. I changed back to 2.2.1 and beacon and validators started properly.\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n2.3.0\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\n```\r\nnote: Some details are omitted, run with `RUST_BACKTRACE=full` for a verbose backtrace.\r\nthread 'main' panicked at 'called `Result::unwrap()` on an `Err` value: Os { code: 1, kind: PermissionDenied, message: \"Operation not permitted\" }', /cargo/registry/src/github.com-1ecc6299db9ec823/slog-async-2.7.0/lib.rs:303:14\r\nstack backtrace:\r\n   0: rust_begin_unwind\r\n             at ./rustc/fe5b13d681f25ee6474be29d748c65adcd91f69e/library/std/src/panicking.rs:584:5\r\n   1: core::panicking::panic_fmt\r\n             at ./rustc/fe5b13d681f25ee6474be29d748c65adcd91f69e/library/core/src/panicking.rs:143:14\r\n   2: core::result::unwrap_failed\r\n             at ./rustc/fe5b13d681f25ee6474be29d748c65adcd91f69e/library/core/src/result.rs:1785:5\r\n   3: slog_async::AsyncBuilder<D>::build\r\n   4: environment::EnvironmentBuilder<E>::initialize_logger\r\n   5: lighthouse::main::{{closure}}\r\n   6: lighthouse::main\r\nnote: Some details are omitted, run with `RUST_BACKTRACE=full` for a verbose backtrace.\r\nthread 'main' panicked at 'called `Result::unwrap()` on an `Err` value: Os { code: 1, kind: PermissionDenied, message: \"Operation not permitted\" }', /cargo/registry/src/github.com-1ecc6299db9ec823/slog-async-2.7.0/lib.rs:303:14\r\nstack backtrace:\r\n   0: rust_begin_unwind\r\n             at ./rustc/fe5b13d681f25ee6474be29d748c65adcd91f69e/library/std/src/panicking.rs:584:5\r\n   1: core::panicking::panic_fmt\r\n             at ./rustc/fe5b13d681f25ee6474be29d748c65adcd91f69e/library/core/src/panicking.rs:143:14\r\n   2: core::result::unwrap_failed\r\n             at ./rustc/fe5b13d681f25ee6474be29d748c65adcd91f69e/library/core/src/result.rs:1785:5\r\n   3: slog_async::AsyncBuilder<D>::build\r\n   4: environment::EnvironmentBuilder<E>::initialize_logger\r\n   5: lighthouse::main::{{closure}}\r\n   6: lighthouse::main\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nUpgrade from 2.2.1 without error\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\n- Synced mainnet beacon chain with validators on same node, both running 2.2.1\r\n- Change version from 2.2.1 to 2.3.0 in docker-compose.yml on both validators and beacon\r\n- Docker compose has depends_on : beacon for validators to start. \r\n- witness logs\r\n",
