    "body": "For anyone looking for a temporary fix, add the following to the `docker-compose.yml` file or find a way to add it to the Docker image provided by the lighthouse team.\r\n\r\nThis may entail security assumptions, make sure you are aware of them before implement it on production\r\n```\r\n    security_opt:\r\n      - \"seccomp:unconfined\"\r\n```",
